{"id":309865,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/global-voices-照片集：菲律宾首都水灾破纪录/","date":"2013-08-22T01:45:59Z","modified":"2013-08-22T01:45:59Z","title":"Global Voices | 照片集：菲律宾首都水灾破纪录","content":"<p><p>菲律宾命名“Maring”的潭美台风，在菲律宾马尼拉大都会区与邻近省份，造成破历史纪录的水灾，有8人死亡、41人受伤与4人失踪。</p>\n<p>根据菲律宾政府的<a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.gov.ph/2013/08/20/ndrrmc-report-effects-of-ts-maring-and-the-southwest-monsoon-august-20-2013-600-p-m/\">报告</a>，有125,348户家庭（602,442人）受台风影响。8月20日晚间，有40,837人仍在198个疏散中心避难。水灾造成65条主要道路无法通行。68个城市约有415处据报淹水。共有162班次的航班（国际航班有59班次，国内航班有103班次），因台风取消。</p>\n<p>菲律宾人使用#maringPH与#floodPH这两个主题标签，监控马尼拉与邻近地区的水灾状况。以下是来自推特与脸书的一些照片，由此可见水灾的状况：</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/WorldVisionPH/status/369708809280696320/photo/1\"><img class=\" wp-image-430411 \" alt=\"Image from World Vision\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/world_vision.png\" width=\"492\" height=\"358\" /></a></p>\n<p>照片来自世界展望会（World Vision）</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/erwinlouis/status/369752075225137152/photo/1\"><img class=\" wp-image-430413 \" alt=\"A flooded village south of Manila. Photo from @erwinlouis\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/bf_homes.png\" width=\"561\" height=\"352\" /></a></p>\n<p>马尼拉南方淹水的村落。照片来自@erwinlouis</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10151668130232739&#038;set=a.10151668128987739.1073741828.745212738&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img class=\" wp-image-430414 \" alt=\"Flood in Marikina, east of Manila. Photo from Facebook page of Prospero De Vera\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/marikina.jpg\" width=\"576\" height=\"432\" /></a></p>\n<p>马尼拉东方马利金纳市（Marikina）的水灾状况。照片来自Prospero De Vera的脸书页面</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10151578812691977&#038;set=a.126333131976.110480.116724526976&#038;type=1&#038;relevant_count=1&#038;ref=nf\"><img class=\" wp-image-430423 \" alt=\"Photo by YouScooper Jefferson Levie, from Facebook page of GMA News \" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/flood-philippines.jpg\" width=\"576\" height=\"381\" /></a></p>\n<p>照片来自GMA News的脸书页面，YouScooper Jefferson Levie拍摄</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10152206187787355&#038;set=a.10150261425492355.331109.197486717354&#038;type=1&#038;relevant_count=1&#038;ref=nf\"><img class=\" wp-image-430415 \" alt=\"A flooded university in Manila. Photo by Salina Teo, from the Facebook page of TomasinoWeb! \" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/ust-flood.png\" width=\"576\" height=\"363\" /></a></p>\n<p>马尼拉一所淹水的大学。照片来自TomasinoWeb!脸书页面，Salina Teo拍摄</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/jamsisante/status/369620918458253312/photo/1\"><img class=\" wp-image-430417 \" alt=\"Knee-deep flood in Manila. Photo by Jam Sisante\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/pup.png\" width=\"543\" height=\"413\" /></a></p>\n<p>马尼拉淹水及膝。Jam Sisante摄</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/siao88/status/369588448950120448/photo/1\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-430418\" alt=\"Flood near the country's main business district. Photo by @siao88 \" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/buendia.png\" width=\"384\" height=\"528\" /></a></p>\n<p>该市主要商业区附近的淹水情形。照片来自@siao88</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/manila_bulletin/status/369242029928091650/photo/1\"><img class=\" wp-image-430420 \" alt=\"Flood near Manila City Hall. Photo by Manila Bulletin\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/manila_flood.png\" width=\"545\" height=\"371\" /></a></p>\n<p>马尼拉市政府附近的淹水情形。照片来自Manila Bulletin</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10151602590555893&#038;set=a.432146415892.201058.302568570892&#038;type=1&#038;relevant_count=1&#038;ref=nf\"><img class=\" wp-image-430421 \" alt=\"Flood in Guagua, north of Manila. Photo from Facebook page of The College Mirror\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/college-mirror.jpg\" width=\"486\" height=\"648\" /></a></p>\n<p>马尼拉北方城市Guagua淹水。照片来自The College Mirror脸书页面</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://twitter.com/PhilippineStar/status/369662269690744832/photo/1\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-430422\" alt=\"Flood in the old downtown of Manila. Photo by Philippine Star\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/lrt.png\" width=\"494\" height=\"356\" /></a></p>\n<p>马尼拉旧城区淹水。照片来自Philippine Star</p>\n</div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://t.co/p5aMe3f3B4\"><img class=\" wp-image-430425 \" alt=\"Flood in Makati, the country's central business district. Photo by Ryan Chua\" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/makati.png\" width=\"582\" height=\"440\" /></a></p>\n<p>马卡蒂（Makati）水患，图为该市的主要商业区。照片来自Ryan Chua</p>\n</div>\n<div>校对者：Rio</div>\n<p><span><span>作者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/author/mong/\" title=\"文章导读 Mong Palatino\">Mong Palatino</a></span> · <span>译者 <a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/author/ameli/\" title=\"文章导读 Ameli\">Ameli</a></span></span>  · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2013/08/21/photos-record-high-floods-in-philippine-capital/\" title=\"阅读原文  en\">阅读原文  en</a></span> · <span><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://zh.globalvoicesonline.org/hans/2013/08/22/12793/#comments\" title=\"则留言\">则留言 (0) </a></span><